{
  "title": "타이머 생성기",
  "content": "[[include :scpko:info:start]]\n**타이머 생성기**\n\n**원본 코드:** [[[https://github.com/scpwiki/timer]]]\n**원 작성자:** [https://gitlab.com/emmiegit Emmie Maeda], [[*user lest-day]], [[*user Wolf20482]], [[*user Dr Lekter]]\n**수정/번역:** [[*user thd-glasses]]\n[[include :scpko:info:end]]\n\n@@@@\n@@@@\n\n+ ,,예시,,\n\n[[div style=\"display: flex; justify-content: space-around; flex-wrap: wrap; width: 100%;\"]]\n[[iframe https://scpko.wdfiles.com/local--code/timer-ko/2?lang=ko&time=2013-01-01T00%3A00%3A00.0000 style=\"width: 280px; height: 70px; border: 0; text-align: center;  left: 50%; position: relative; transform: translateX(-50%);\"]]\n\n[[iframe https://scpko.wdfiles.com/local--code/timer-ko/2?lang=ko&time=2033-01-01T00%3A00%3A00.0000 style=\"width: 280px; height: 70px; border: 0; text-align: center;  left: 50%; position: relative; transform: translateX(-50%);\"]]\n[[/div]]\n\n@@@@\n@@@@\n\n+ ,,생성기,,\n[[iframe https://scpko.wdfiles.com/local--code/timer-ko/1?lang=ko width=\"100%\" height=\"800px\" frameborder=\"1\"]]\n\n@@@@\n@@@@\n\n+ ,,사용 방법,,\n\n* **타이머 종류:** __범용__은 단일한 타이머 아이프레임을 생성합니다. __병렬 열기/닫기__는 타이머 두 개를 가로로 나란히 배치할 수 있도록 감싸주는 flex div를 같이 생성합니다. 병렬 타이머의 타이틀은 번역 검토 절차에 맞춰져 있으므로 기타 용도로 사용할 경우 __지시문__을 수정해주세요.\n* **시작 시점:** __생성기 사용 시점__ 또는 __선택한 시점__으로부터 기간을 산정하도록 설정합니다.\n* **기간:** 시작 시점으로부터 __얼마 후에 타이머가 종료할지__ 설정합니다.\n* **지시문:** 타이머의 __타이틀__을 설정합니다. 미입력시 기본값을 따릅니다.\n* **고급**\n * **높이/폭:** 타이머 아이프레임의 크기를 설정합니다. 미입력시 기본값을 따릅니다.\n * **커스텀 타이머 CSS:** 타이머에 적용할 CSS 속성을 추가 설정합니다.\n * **표출 템플릿:** 아이프레임을 포함해 입력이 필요한 텍스트를 설정 및 확인할 수 있습니다.\n* **타이머 생성:** 설정한 값들을 이용해 새 타이머를 생성합니다. 생성된 구문을 복사해서 한국어 위키 내의 원하는 위치에 부착하면 타이머가 생성됩니다. 병렬 타이머를 생성한 경우 반드시 열기/닫기를 짝지어서 사용해주세요.\n\n@@@@\n@@@@\n\n+ ,,소스코드,,\n\n[*https://scpko.wdfiles.com/local--files/timer-ko/timer-selector-ko.js timer-selector-ko.js (file)]\n[*https://scpko.wdfiles.com/local--files/timer-ko/timer-ko.js timer-ko.js (file)]\n\n[[collapsible show=\"timer-selector-ko.html\" hide=\"timer-selector-ko.html\"]]\n[[code type=\"html\"]]\n<!DOCTYPE html>\n<html>\n  <head>\n    <meta charset=\"UTF-8\">\n    <meta name=\"description\" content=\"SCP Wiki Timer Selector\">\n    <meta name=\"keywords\" content=\"scp,wiki,timer,selector,generator\">\n    <link rel=\"stylesheet\" href=\"https://scpwiki.github.io/timer/timer-selector.css\">\n    <script src=\"https://scpko.wdfiles.com/local--files/timer-ko/timer-selector-ko.js\"></script>\n    <title>Timer Selector</title>\n  </head>\n\n  <body>\n    <noscript>This application requires Javascript to function.</noscript>\n\n    <h1 id=\"error\" class=\"hidden\"></h1>\n\n    <div id=\"form\">\n      <fieldset id=\"timer-type\">\n        <legend id=\"timer-type-label\"></legend>\n\n        <!-- Generic -->\n        <span>\n          <input id=\"timer-type-generic\" type=\"radio\" name=\"timer-type\" value=\"generic\" checked>\n          <label id=\"timer-type-generic-label\" for=\"timer-type\"></label>\n        </span>\n\n        <!-- Deletion -->\n        <span>\n          <input id=\"timer-type-deletion\" type=\"radio\" name=\"timer-type\" value=\"deletion\">\n          <label id=\"timer-type-deletion-label\" for=\"timer-type\"></label>\n        </span>\n\n        <!-- Ban -->\n        <span>\n          <input id=\"timer-type-ban\" type=\"radio\" name=\"timer-type\" value=\"ban\">\n          <label id=\"timer-type-ban-label\" for=\"timer-type\"></label>\n        </span>\n      </fieldset>\n\n      <fieldset id=\"start\">\n        <legend id=\"start-label\"></legend>\n\n        <!-- now -->\n        <span>\n          <input id=\"start-now\" type=\"radio\" name=\"start\" value=\"now\" checked>\n          <label id=\"start-now-label\" for=\"now\"></label>\n        </span>\n\n        <!-- later / other time -->\n        <span>\n          <input id=\"start-later\" type=\"radio\" name=\"start\" value=\"later\">\n          <label id=\"start-later-label\" for=\"later\"></label>\n          <input id=\"start-later-date\" class=\"radio-text\" type=\"date\"></input>\n          <input id=\"start-later-time\" class=\"radio-text\" type=\"time\"></input>\n        </span>\n      </fieldset>\n\n      <fieldset id=\"duration\">\n        <legend id=\"duration-label\"></legend>\n\n        <!-- 1 day -->\n        <span>\n          <input id=\"duration-1d\" type=\"radio\" name=\"duration\" value=\"86400000\" checked>\n          <label id=\"duration-1d-label\" for=\"86400000\"></label> <!-- in ms -->\n        </span>\n\n        <!-- 3 day -->\n        <span>\n          <input id=\"duration-3d\" type=\"radio\" name=\"duration\" value=\"259200000\" checked>\n          <label id=\"duration-3d-label\" for=\"259200000\"></label>\n        </span>\n\n        <!-- 1 week -->\n        <span>\n          <input id=\"duration-1w\" type=\"radio\" name=\"duration\" value=\"604800000\">\n          <label id=\"duration-1w-label\" for=\"604800000\"></label>\n        </span>\n\n        <!-- 2 weeks -->\n        <span>\n          <input id=\"duration-2w\" type=\"radio\" name=\"duration\" value=\"1209600000\">\n          <label id=\"duration-2w-label\" for=\"1209600000\"></label>\n        </span>\n\n        <!-- 1 year -->\n        <span>\n          <input id=\"duration-1y\" type=\"radio\" name=\"duration\" value=\"31536000000\">\n          <label id=\"duration-1y-label\" for=\"31536000000\"></label>\n        </span>\n\n        <!-- custom -->\n        <span>\n          <input id=\"duration-custom\" type=\"radio\" name=\"duration\" value=\"custom\">\n          <label id=\"duration-custom-label\" for=\"custom\"></label>\n          <input id=\"duration-custom-value\" class=\"radio-text\" type=\"number\" size=\"6\"></input>\n          <select id=\"duration-custom-unit\">\n            <option id=\"unit-minute\" value=\"60000\"></option>\n            <option id=\"unit-hour\" value=\"3600000\"></option>\n            <option id=\"unit-day\" value=\"86400000\"></option>\n            <option id=\"unit-week\" value=\"604800000\"></option>\n            <option id=\"unit-month\" value=\"2592000000\"></option>\n            <option id=\"unit-year\" value=\"31536000000\"></option>\n          </select>\n        </span>\n      </fieldset>\n\n      <fieldset id=\"messages\">\n        <legend id=\"messages-label\"></legend>\n\n        <div class=\"text\">\n          <label id=\"message-progress-label\"></label>\n          <input id=\"message-progress\" type=\"text\"></input>\n        </div>\n\n        <div class=\"text\">\n          <label id=\"message-finished-label\"></label>\n          <input id=\"message-finished\" type=\"text\"></input>\n        </div>\n      </fieldset>\n\n      <fieldset id=\"advanced\">\n        <legend id=\"advanced-label\"></legend>\n\n        <div class=\"text message-short\">\n          <label id=\"height-label\"></label>\n          <input id=\"height\" type=\"text\" value=\"70px\"></input>\n        </div>\n\n        <div class=\"text message-short\">\n          <label id=\"width-label\"></label>\n          <input id=\"width\" type=\"text\" value=\"280px\"></input>\n        </div>\n\n        <div class=\"text\">\n          <label id=\"custom-css-label\"></label><br>\n          <textarea id=\"custom-css\" cols=\"60\" rows=\"4\"></textarea>\n        </div>\n\n        <div class=\"text\">\n          <label id=\"template-label\"></label><br>\n          <textarea id=\"template\" cols=\"60\" rows=\"4\">%%iframe%%</textarea>\n        </div>\n      </fieldset>\n\n      <div>\n        <button id=\"build\"></button>\n\n        <span class=\"info\">\n          [<a id=\"info-help\" href=\"https://scpwiki.github.io/timer\" target=\"_blank\"></a>]\n          [<a id=\"info-source\" href=\"https://github.com/scpwiki/timer\" target=\"_blank\"></a>]\n        </span>\n      </div>\n    </div>\n\n    <!-- output -->\n    <div><textarea id=\"output\" class=\"hidden\" cols=\"60\" rows=\"4\" readonly></textarea></div>\n  </body>\n</html>\n\n[[/code]]\n[[/collapsible]]\n[[collapsible show=\"timer-ko.html\" hide=\"timer-ko.html\"]]\n[[code type=\"html\"]]\n<!DOCTYPE html>\n<html>\n  <head>\n    <meta charset=\"UTF-8\">\n    <meta name=\"description\" content=\"SCP Wiki Timer instance\">\n    <meta name=\"keywords\" content=\"scp,wiki,timer\">\n    <link rel=\"stylesheet\" href=\"https://scpko.wdfiles.com/local--code/timer-ko/3\">\n    <script src=\"https://scpko.wdfiles.com/local--files/timer-ko/timer-ko.js\"></script>\n    <title>Timer (initializing...)</title>\n  </head>\n\n  <body>\n    <noscript>This application requires Javascript to function.</noscript>\n\n    <div id=\"timer\">\n      <h2 id=\"title\"></h2>\n\n      <div id=\"clock\">\n        <div id=\"years-div\" class=\"unit\">\n          <span id=\"years\" class=\"unit-value\"></span>\n          <span id=\"years-label\" class=\"unit-label\"></span>\n        </div>\n\n        <div id=\"months-div\" class=\"unit\">\n          <span id=\"months\" class=\"unit-value\"></span>\n          <span id=\"months-label\" class=\"unit-label\"></span>\n        </div>\n\n        <div id=\"days-div\" class=\"unit\">\n          <span id=\"days\" class=\"unit-value\"></span>\n          <span id=\"days-label\" class=\"unit-label\"></span>\n        </div>\n\n        <div id=\"hours-div\" class=\"unit\">\n          <span id=\"hours\" class=\"unit-value\"></span>\n          <span id=\"hours-label\" class=\"unit-label\"></span>\n        </div>\n\n        <div id=\"minutes-div\" class=\"unit\">\n          <span id=\"minutes\" class=\"unit-value\"></span>\n          <span id=\"minutes-label\" class=\"unit-label\"></span>\n        </div>\n\n        <div id=\"seconds-div\" class=\"unit\">\n          <span id=\"seconds\" class=\"unit-value\"></span>\n          <span id=\"seconds-label\" class=\"unit-label\"></span>\n        </div>\n      </div>\n    </div>\n  </body>\n</html>\n[[/code]]\n[[/collapsible]]\n[*https://github.com/scpwiki/timer/blob/main/timer-selector.css timer-selector.css (git)]\n[[collapsible show=\"timer-ko.css\" hide=\"timer-ko.css\"]]\n[[code type=\"CSS\"]]\n\n@import url('https://fonts.googleapis.com/earlyaccess/nanumgothiccoding.css');\n\n/* Main elements */\n\nhtml {\n  height: 100%;\n}\n\nbody {\n  margin: 0;\n  height: 100%;\n  font-family: 'Nanum Gothic Coding', Arial, sans-serif;\n  overflow: hidden;\n}\n\n#timer {\n  transform: translateY(calc(50vh - 30%));\n}\n\n#title {\n  font-size: 0.8em;\n  line-height: 0;\n  position: absolute;\n  top: -1.5em;\n  left: 0;\n}\n\n#clock {\n  text-align: center;\n  background-color: #eee;\n  padding: 0.15em;\n  margin: 0 auto;\n  width: 100%;\n}\n\n.unit {\n  display: inline-block;\n  margin: 0 0.25em;\n}\n\n.unit-value {\n  font-family: 'Nanum Gothic Coding',  'Droid Sans Mono', 'DejaVu Sans Mono', monospace;\n  font-size: 1.3em;\n  font-weight: 900;\n  background-color: #ddd;\n  border-radius: 0.25em;\n  padding: 0.1em;\n}\n\n.unit-label {\n  font-size: 0.8em;\n}\n\n/* Basic utility classes */\n.hidden {\n  display: none;\n}\n\n.error {\n  color: #b01;\n}\n\n.error-secondary {\n  font-size: 0.6em;\n}\n\n.progress {\n  color: black;\n}\n\n.finished {\n  color: #282;\n}\n\n[[/code]]\n[[/collapsible]]",
